channel.title: (317) 4Youscape V1 (317)
channel.description:
Hello Moparscapers, Yesterday I wanted to code a good 317 source and.. I did I call it 4Youscape V1.
[b]CREDITS[/b]: Stormcutter 50% for base 50% To me for coding.
[b]LINKS[/b] [b][i]Server link: http://uppit.com/v/C4B5MLKU[/i][/b] [b][i]Client link: http://www.megaupload.com/?d=1U4HC5JV[/i][/b]
[b][i]COMMANDS: Player commands: ::players ::help ::pure ::starter ::home ::edge ::pk [b]::train[/b]
Mod commands: ::kick [NAME] ::mute [NAME] ::ipmute [NAME]
Admin commands: ::banuser [NAME] ::kick [NAME] ::mute [NAME] ::ipmute [NAME] ::ipban [NAME] ::xteleto [NAME] ::xteletome [NAME] ::tele [COORDS] (Example ::tele 3288 2777)
Owner commands: ::xteleall ::xteletome [NAME] ::xteleto [NAME] ::ipban [NAME] ::banuser [NAME] ::mute [NAME] ::ipmute [NAME] ::hourmute [NAME] (Example ::hourmute Test 1 (The 1 is 1 hour) ::kick [NAME] ::hail
FEATURES: Jad, KQ, Ancient mini, GS mini, Barrows, Edge 1 vs 1 pk, Pk team pk, and much more!
